@TestCases:
End-to-end: parses an empty class, runs translate_to_hir, and asserts the
resulting HIR pointer is non-null. Locks down the trivial happy path
through the Java->HIR pipeline.
@End TestCases
Process called "test_java_to_hir_class" returns Integer:
    Note: Test Java to HIR class translation

